<div id="meet-the-soldiers" class="container-fluid">
  <h2 class="py-5 text-center underline"><strong>MEET THE SOLDIERS</strong></h2>

  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-6">
      <p class="text-justify">
      What started off as a local initiative of the New York Upper East Side Jewish
      community has now become a global movement, dedicated to helping veterans of the 
      IDF reintegrate into civilian life with the love and support they need to thrive. 
      In 2018, a south Florida trip sparked an inititive by the Las Olas Chabbad due 
      to the passion and Jewish and Israeli values of our community. We are honored 
      to bring another twelve wounded Israeli soldiers in 2019 to our community for 
      a warm embrace and healing - South Florida style.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-6">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <h3 class="text-center underline pt-5">Learn About Our Impact on Our 2018 Soldiers</h3>
        <div class="row text-center justify-content-center">
          {{#each soldiers2018}}
            {{> soldierPartial this}}
            {{#if_odd @index}}
              <div class="w-100"></div>    
            {{/if_odd}}
          {{/each}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-6">
      <h3 class="text-center underline pt-5">Create and Feel the Impact on Our 2019 Soldiers</h3>
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row text-center justify-content-center">
          {{#each soldiers2019}}
            {{> soldierPartial this}}
            {{#if_odd @index}}
              <div class="w-100"></div>    
            {{/if_odd}}
          {{/each}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

